OL,3,CWhy some passengers have been getting
OL,4,Cfree bus rides in Guernsey
OL,6,FSome Guernsey passengers have been
OL,7,Ftravelling on the bus for free
OL,8,Ffollowing a payment system fault.
OL,10,FThe bus operator, Stagecoach, says it
OL,11,Fis working to resolve the issue, but
OL,12,Fhas not specified the amount of
OL,13,Frevenue lost since the issue was
OL,14,Fflagged last week.
OL,16,FIt is also unclear when the issue will
OL,17,Fbe fixed and there are concerns over
OL,18,Fthe impact of lost revenue,
OL,19,Fparticularly the cost to taxpayers who
OL,20,Fhelp fund the service.
