OL,3,CWhy some passengers have been getting
OL,4,Cfree bus rides in Guernsey
OL,6,FFormer Guernsey politician Mary Lowe
OL,7,Fsays: "The States should be concerned
OL,8,Fthat they haven't been made aware that
OL,9,Ftheir figures aren't going to be
OL,10,Faccurate.
OL,12,F"You and I, as taxpayers who put money
OL,13,Finto the buses, should know what is
OL,14,Fgoing on, because it's costing us
OL,15,Fmoney, and it's not as if the island
OL,16,Fis very rich at the moment."
