OL,3,CWhy some passengers have been getting
OL,4,Cfree bus rides in Guernsey
OL,6,FMary says she noticed the issue
OL,7,Fseveral days ago, adding: "It's not
OL,8,Fall the buses, but I was on the five
OL,9,Fo'clock bus, and it's full, people are
OL,10,Fstanding, visitors, locals, and yet
OL,11,Fnobody's paid, so they have lost a lot
OL,12,Fof money.
OL,14,F"We usually have the figures from the
OL,15,Fbus company, how many passengers, how
OL,16,Fmuch money the bus company has taken,
OL,17,Fand now we aren't going to have that
OL,18,Fbecause it hasn't been registering on
OL,19,Fthe ticket machine."
