OL,3,CWhy some passengers have been getting
OL,4,Cfree bus rides in Guernsey
OL,6,FIn a statement, Stagecoach says: "We
OL,7,Fare aware that a number of on-bus
OL,8,Fticket machines in Guernsey are
OL,9,Fcurrently affected by a technical
OL,10,Fissue linked to the Ticketer system
OL,11,Fused across the network.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with Ticketer
OL,14,Fto help them resolve it as quickly as
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,F"We would like to thank our customers
OL,18,Ffor their patience and understanding
OL,19,Fwhile Ticketer works to implement a
OL,20,Ffix."
