OL,3,CWhy some passengers have been getting
OL,4,Cfree bus rides in Guernsey
OL,6,FLaura Oxburgh, Head of On-Island
OL,7,FTravel for the States of Guernsey,
OL,8,Fadds: "It was brought to our attention
OL,9,Fthat on Friday, a small number of bus
OL,10,Fticketing machines were experiencing
OL,11,Ferrors.
OL,13,F"Stagecoach has investigated the
OL,14,Fcause, and it is now understood they
OL,15,Fwere the result of a software issue
OL,16,Ffollowing an update administered by
OL,17,Fthe system provider, Ticketer.
OL,19,F"Stagecoach is working with Ticketer
OL,20,Fto urgently resolve the matter."
